TO ADD NEW PARKRUN RESULTS TO SOURCE DATA

Easiest

1. copy last run
2. add to file "rawdata/raw_results.csv"


Easiest if want to redo all

1. screenshot latest results
2. go to https://extracttable.com/
3. download csv and move to rawdata/
